

* Added spanish layout to keyboard a key combo away.

used setxkbmap and localectl for that.
localectl list-x11-keymap-models lists keyboard models
localectl list-x11-keymap-layout for langauge
localectl list-x11-keymap-variant <language>   for variant of that language
localectl list-x11-keymap-options for options to choose from
and use the choosing with setxkbmap

setxkbmap -model dell -layout es -variant mac -option ctrl:nocaps